Only right to start the year off with destruction 
.
.
.
Donor removal for a midsole swap.
.
.
For those that are unaware, there are only 2 choices for donors for a Nike yeezy 1. 
.
Either a Nike revolution (which are old and hard to come by) 
.
or a replica pair of yeezy 1s (newer midsole but expensive)
.
 Pick your poison, either way the midsoles the same
.
.
Happy new year everyone 
.
.
